Achieve consistency in Axiom documentation and in-app content. Follow [Google style guide](https://developers.google.com/style) unless noted otherwise.

## Voice & Tone
- **Primary:** Simplicity, conciseness, speed. Inspired by [Simplified Technical English](https://www.asd-ste100.org/).
- **Secondary:** Appealing and playful—but never at the expense of clarity.

## Scope
Document Axiom only. Don't document third-party products (they change without notice). Link to external docs instead—never to competitors.

## Doc Structure
1. **Concept** – Goals, terms (optional), section links
2. **Prerequisites** (optional)
3. **Procedures** – Self-contained steps with code examples
4. **Limitations** (optional)
5. **Reference** (optional) – API links, additional options
6. **What's Next** – Related pages

