# Code & Graphics

## Code Snippets
- Use simple, self-contained examples
- Add comments above goal-specific lines

## Screenshots
- Use many in getting started guides
- Use sparingly elsewhere (UI changes often, hard to maintain)
- Don't screenshot copyable text

## Diagrams
- One-direction arrows unless bidirectional is necessary
- Simple descriptions
- Follow [Lucidchart UML](https://www.lucidchart.com/pages/uml-class-diagram)
- Consult Design team

