# Placeholders

| Type | Format | Example |
|------|--------|---------|
| API path parameters | lowercase, `_` separator, `{}` | `v1/datasets/{dataset_name}` |
| Other placeholders | UPPERCASE, `_` separator | `DATASET_NAME` |

Distinguish placeholders from variable names: `AXIOM_API_TOKEN = "<YOUR_API_TOKEN>"` (variable) vs `Bearer <AXIOM_API_TOKEN>` (placeholder).
